 \"from\": 530, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"targets\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"obscure oddities\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) has now taken a significant step forward in its esports push by officially approving the creation of the Olympic Esports Games, although the games involved are still not what you'd expect.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a significant step\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"its esports\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 752}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The standalone event is set to take place in 2025 in Saudi Arabia, which is currently hosting thefirst ever Esports World Cup.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 1013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 952, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.9999994907622227, \"rank\": 5.087401884433935e-07, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The standalone event\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"thefirst\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"Esports World Cup\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An exact date and venue is yet to be decided, but it comes as part of a 12-year agreement between the IOC and the country to host the event.\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1116, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.848615220702012e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An exact date\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"venue\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"a 12-year agreement\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Esports Games will act as a standalone event outside of the actual Olympics, and it's currently unclear whether winners will actually receive medals (participants in the Olympic Esports Series last year won small trophies instead).\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1399, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.59242523599314e-34, \"text\": \"Esports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a standalone event\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"the actual Olympics\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1243}, {\"ngram\": \"winners\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1330}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Series\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"small trophies\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up to theGameCentral newsletterfor a unique take on the week in gaming, alongside the latest reviews and more.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theGameCentral\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique take\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"gaming\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest reviews\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Delivered to your inbox every Saturday morning.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking about the announcement, IOC president Thomas Bach said: 'This is truly a new era for the IOC.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.848615220702012e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.848615220702012e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"a new era\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the confirmation by the IOC Session of the creation of the Olympic Esports Games, we are keeping up with the pace of the digital revolution.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the confirmation\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC Session\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Games\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"the digital revolution\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee have unanimously voted yes for the creation of the Olympic Esports Gamespic.twitter.com/JIhEFJITCQ 'The esports community, represented in our Esports Commission, has enthusiastically engaged with this initiative.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 2065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1820, \"end\": 1851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.59242523599314e-34, \"text\": \"Esports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Esports Gamespic.twitter.com/JIhEFJITCQ\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"The esports community\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"this initiative\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is further proof of the attractivity of the Olympic brand and the values it stands for among young people.'\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"further proof\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2087}, {\"ngram\": \"the attractivity\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic brand\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"the values\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for what games could be on the line-up, do not expect any first person shooters.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what games\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"the line-up\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"any first person shooters\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOCpreviously statedgames likeCounter-Strike, Call Of Duty, and Rainbow Six Siege, will 'never be part of Olympic Esports' as they involve 'visible violence' using weapons.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The IOCpreviously statedgames\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"likeCounter-Strike\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"Call\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"Duty\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"Rainbow Six Siege\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Esports\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"'visible violence\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2424}, {\"ngram\": \"weapons\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's unclear though if this stance extends to fighting games likeStreet Fighter 6.\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this stance\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"fighting\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2502}, {\"ngram\": \"Fighter\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Capcom's fighter was part of a separate exhibition event during Olympic Esports Week last year, but it was omitted from the main Olympics Esports Series line-up.\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2525, \"end\": 2531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capcom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0988263940524066e-22, \"text\": \"Capcom\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capcom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Capcom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"a separate exhibition event\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Esports Week\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"the main Olympics Esports Series line-up\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No one in the IOC seems willing to acknowledge that the games featured in last year's event have little or no competitive community around them, with several being so obscure most people have never heard of them.\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.848615220702012e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's event\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"little or no competitive community\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like if you replaced actual Olympic sports with Tiddlywinks and an egg and spoon race, and seems hypocritical given sports such as boxing and karate have been part of the Olympics for decades.\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2955, \"end\": 2966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiddlywinks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tiddlywinks\", \"types\": [\"Q1914636\", \"Q11410\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiddlywinks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiddlywinks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"actual Olympic sports\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2949}, {\"ngram\": \"an egg\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"given sports\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3029}, {\"ngram\": \"boxing\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3044}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has entered a new era with the creation of the Olympic Esports Games, with the first-ever edition being held in Saudi Arabia in 2025, as the proposal was endorsed by the IOC executive board unanimously.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3105, \"end\": 3108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.848615220702012e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3227, \"end\": 3233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.9999994907622227, \"rank\": 5.087401884433935e-07, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 3279, \"end\": 3282, \"tit